#. Plugin Name of the plugin/theme
msgid "WP PureSMTP"
msgstr "WP PureSMTP"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin/theme
msgid "https://github.com/Steffenkt/WP-PureSMTP"
msgstr "https://github.com/Steffenkt/WP-PureSMTP"

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid "Replace WordPress default mail with a clean, pure SMTP connection. No third-party APIs, no bloat — just SMTP."
msgstr "Ersetzt die Standard-WordPress-E-Mail durch eine saubere, reine SMTP-Verbindung. Keine Drittanbieter-APIs, kein Ballast – nur SMTP."

#. Author of the plugin/theme
msgid "Steffenkt"
msgstr "Steffenkt"

